<subSubSection box="[199,1271,916,943]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,916,1195]" box="[199,1271,916,943]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,328,916,942]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">Etymology</emphasis>
. The name of this species refers to the Anstiranana Province where it was collected.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="395" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,916,1195]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,328,951,978]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">Comments</emphasis>
. This species differs from 
<taxonomicName authority="Duarte Rodrigues" authorityName="Duarte Rodrigues" authorityYear="1992" box="[635,962,952,979]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Haedacanthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="decoris">
<emphasis box="[635,753,952,978]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">H. decoris</emphasis>
Duarte Rodrigues
</taxonomicName>
having a costal area three to four areolae wide, narrowing to two areolae wide on subcostal area near swollen part. It also differs from 
<taxonomicName authority="(Drake)" baseAuthorityName="Drake" baseAuthorityYear="1958" box="[1182,1390,988,1015]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Haedacanthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="crispus">
<emphasis box="[1182,1296,989,1014]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">H. crispus</emphasis>
(Drake)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="(Drake)" baseAuthorityName="Drake" baseAuthorityYear="1958" box="[151,371,1024,1051]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Haedacanthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="heranus">
<emphasis box="[151,276,1024,1050]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">H. heranus</emphasis>
(Drake)
</taxonomicName>
by the costal area four to five areolae wide in 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Drake" baseAuthorityYear="1958" box="[897,1013,1025,1050]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Haedacanthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="crispus">
<emphasis box="[897,1013,1025,1050]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">H. crispus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and five to six in 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Drake" baseAuthorityYear="1958" box="[1218,1343,1024,1050]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Haedacanthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="heranus">
<emphasis box="[1218,1343,1024,1050]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">H. heranus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and by the subcostal area also smaller than the one of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Drake" baseAuthorityYear="1958" box="[673,797,1060,1086]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Haedacanthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="heranus">
<emphasis box="[673,797,1060,1086]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">H. heranus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(two areolae wide).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,916,1195]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">
The genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Duarte Rodrigues" authorityYear="1992" box="[330,492,1096,1122]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Haedacanthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[330,492,1096,1122]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">Haedacanthus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Duarte Rodrigues, P." box="[716,1004,1096,1123]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" refId="ref7087" refString="Duarte Rodrigues, P. (1992) Insectes Heteropteres Tingidae. Faune de Madagascar. Fasc. 78. Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle, Paris, 94 S." type="book" year="1992">Duarte Rodrigues (1992)</bibRefCitation>
to accommodate 
<taxonomicName authority="(Drake 1958)" baseAuthorityName="Drake" baseAuthorityYear="1958" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Pogonostyla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="crispa">
<emphasis box="[1215,1436,1096,1122]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">Pogonostyla crispa</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Drake, C. J." box="[159,294,1131,1158]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" pagination="315 - 333" refId="ref6974" refString="Drake, C. J. (1958) Quelques Tingidae malgaches (Hemiptera). Memoires de l'Institut scientifique de Madagascar, Serie E, 9, 315 - 333." type="journal article" year="1958">Drake 1958</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName authority="(Drake 1958)" baseAuthorityName="Drake" baseAuthorityYear="1958" box="[310,579,1131,1158]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Pogonostyla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="herana">
<emphasis box="[310,417,1132,1158]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">P. herana</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Drake, C. J." box="[433,570,1131,1158]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" pagination="315 - 333" refId="ref6974" refString="Drake, C. J. (1958) Quelques Tingidae malgaches (Hemiptera). Memoires de l'Institut scientifique de Madagascar, Serie E, 9, 315 - 333." type="journal article" year="1958">Drake 1958</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Duarte Rodrigues 1992" authorityName="Duarte Rodrigues" authorityYear="1992" box="[640,1031,1132,1159]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Haedacanthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="decoris">
<emphasis box="[640,757,1132,1158]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">H. decoris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Duarte Rodrigues, P." box="[765,1031,1132,1159]" pageId="4" pageNumber="395" refId="ref7087" refString="Duarte Rodrigues, P. (1992) Insectes Heteropteres Tingidae. Faune de Madagascar. Fasc. 78. Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle, Paris, 94 S." type="book" year="1992">Duarte Rodrigues 1992</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. The genus is endemic to 
<collectingCountry name="Madagascar" pageId="4" pageNumber="395">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
